(101, NULL, 'Dredd Song', 'Otros II', 'BSO Judge Dredd', '<p>Never say it''s over<br />\r\n  Never say the end<br />\r\n  Anytime you stop just start again<br />\r\n  Never say give up<br />\r\n  Never say give in<br />\r\nYou always have to fight to win</p>\r\n<p>However much it hurts<br />\r\n  However much it takes<br />\r\n  Believe and all your dreams will all come true<br />\r\n  However hard it gets<br />\r\n  However much it aches<br />\r\n  Always believe in me<br />\r\n  As i believe in you</p>\r\n<p>To never say too late<br />\r\n  Never say it''s done<br />\r\n  Make me know for real you are the one<br />\r\n  The one that never turns<br />\r\n  Never walks away<br />\r\n  The one that i can trust to always stay</p>\r\n<p>Never say surrender<br />\r\n  Never say die<br />\r\n  You only ever get there if you try<br />\r\n  Never say give up<br />\r\n  Never say give in<br />\r\n  You always have to fight to win</p>\r\n<p>However much it hurts<br />\r\n  However much it takes<br />\r\n  Believe that all your dreams can all come true<br />\r\n  However hard it gets<br />\r\n  However much it aches<br />\r\n  Always believe in me<br />\r\n  As i believe in you</p>\r\n<p>Never say if only<br />\r\n  Never say regret<br />\r\n  Only the weak remember to forget<br />\r\n  Never say it''s over<br />\r\n  Never say the end<br />\r\n  Never say never again</p>\r\n<p>However much it hurts<br />\r\n  However much it takes<br />\r\n  Believe and all your dreams will all come true<br />\r\n  However hard it gets<br />\r\n  However much it aches<br />\r\n  Believe in me<br />\r\n  As i believe in you </p>', ''),
(12, 1989, 'Fear of ghosts', 'Disintegration', NULL, '<p>Like a feeling that I''m down<br />\r\n  Deep inside my heart<br />\r\n  Like I''m looking out through<br />\r\n  Splitting blood red<br />\r\n  Windows in my heart<br />\r\n  From a higher up than heaven<br />\r\n  And a harder down than stone<br />\r\n  Shake the fear that always clawing<br />\r\n  Pulls me clawing down alone<br />\r\n  As I spitting splitting blood red<br />\r\n  Breaking windows in my heart<br />\r\n  And the past is taunting<br />\r\n  Fear of ghosts<br />\r\n  Is forcing me apart<br />\r\n  And the further I get<br />\r\n  From the things that I care about<br />\r\n  The less I care about<br />\r\n  How much further away I get...</p>\r\n<p>I am lost again<br />\r\n  With everything gone<br />\r\n  And more alone<br />\r\n  Than I have ever been<br />\r\n  I expect you to understand<br />\r\n  To feel it too<br />\r\n  But I know that even if you will<br />\r\n  You cannot ever help me<br />\r\n  Nor can I<br />\r\n  Ever help you</p>', '<p>Como un sentimiento de que me hundo<br />\r\n  Profundamente dentro de mi coraz&oacute;n<br />\r\n  Como si buscara a trav&eacute;s<br />\r\n  De astilladas ventanas<br />\r\n  rojo sangre en mi coraz&oacute;n<br />\r\n  Desde m&aacute;s arriba que el cielo<br />\r\n  Y m&aacute;s duramente abajo que una piedra<br />\r\n  Me sacudo el miedo que siempre ara&ntilde;a<br />\r\n  Me empuja ara&ntilde;&aacute;ndome solo<br />\r\n  Mientras escupo astilladas ventanas rojo sangre<br />\r\n  Rotas en mi coraz&oacute;n<br />\r\n  Y el pasado est&aacute; reprochando<br />\r\n  El miedo a los fantasmas<br />\r\n  me est&aacute; forzando a separarme<br />\r\n  Y como m&aacute;s me alejo<br />\r\n  De las cosas que me preocupan<br />\r\n  Menos me preocupa<br />\r\nCu&aacute;nto me alejo...</p>\r\n<p>Estoy perdido otra vez<br />\r\n  Con todo desaparecido<br />\r\n  Y m&aacute;s solo<br />\r\n  de lo que he estado jam&aacute;s<br />\r\n  Yo espero que t&uacute; lo 