(101, NULL, 'Happy birthday', 'Otros II', NULL, '<p>Those down days<br />\r\n  When you felt so young<br />\r\n  And everything seemed</p>\r\n<p>You saw the people<br />\r\n  Around you<br />\r\n  Getting old</p>\r\n<p>You wake up<br />\r\n  The teenage yearn is<br />\r\n  Gone for you</p>\r\n<p>It happens to others<br />\r\n  It happens all the time<br />\r\n  Happy birthday to you<br />\r\n  Happy birthday to you<br />\r\n  Happy birthday to you</p>\r\n<p>The candles on the cake<br />\r\n  Waiting to be blown<br />\r\n  Wish I was<br />\r\n  An other</p>', ''),
